description: One-of-a-kind design meets prime South Boston living in this re-priced, bright corner condo. Soaring ceilings, expansive windows, and a sleek double-sided fireplace define the open layout, blending style and comfort with a flexible dining area, generous living room, and bonus nook for a home office, studio, or reading space. The chef’s kitchen features custom Henrybuilt cabinetry, Dornbracht fixtures, and iconic Fritz Hansen lighting in a clean, contemporary finish. The primary suite offers a walk-in closet with built-ins, while the second bedroom adapts easily to multiple uses. In-unit laundry, central air, abundant storage, and direct-access garage parking add everyday convenience. With its unique layout, modern design, and coveted East Side location near parks, restaurants, and transit, this residence delivers elevated city living.
